<SceneText>
  <Speakers>
    <Section>Speaker</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ユーリ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yuri</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>24</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>フレン</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Flynn</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>25</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>連れてけよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Take me away.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>24</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ユーリ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yuri...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>25</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>言っただろ？
裁かれる覚悟は出来てるってよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I told you, didn't I?
I'm prepared for my judgement.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>24</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>それに、いいもんが聞けた。
オレの覚悟がお前の覚悟を
呼び寄せたってなら、悪くねぇ結末だ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Plus, what I heard from you was a good thing.
If my resolve brought your resolve to the surface,
this isn't a bad conclusion.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>24</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>その代わり、最後の言葉、絶対に忘れんなよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>In exchange, make sure you
never forget my last words.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>24</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>もちろんだ。
僕は君とは違う道を貫き通してみせる</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Of course. I will persist with my path,
that which is different from yours.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>25</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>その上で、間違えた道を選んだ君を
ずっと責め続け、でもだからこそ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Moreover, I've always criticized you for
choosing the wrong path, but that's why...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>25</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>親友として、尊敬し続けるよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I will continue to respect you as my dearest friend.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>25</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>お前はホント……甘いよな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You really are... naive, y'know.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>24</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>でも、そうだな。
甘くて堅物だが、信じてやるよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But you're right.
You're naive and stubborn, but I believe in you.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>24</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>あとは任せたぜ、フレン</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I'll leave the rest to you, Flynn.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>24</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>やってみせるさ。
もう君のような者が現れないようにね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I'll show you.
Nobody like you will have to appear again.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>25</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ああ、オレで最後にしろ。
こんな奴はな……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yeah. Make it so I'm the last one.
The last one who has to be like this...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>24</SpeakerId>
      <Id>14</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
